Documentation
=============
- manpages for splash_util, splash_manager and splash_geninitramfs
- automatic generation of ChangeLogs

Fixes
=====
- render: move all sanity checks (position on screen) to bndrect calculation
- handle DIRECTCOLOR modes in libsplashrender
- handle KDGRAPHICS in libsplashrender (?)

New features
============
- automatic theme resizing
- add effects (fadein/fadeout/blendin) for icon/anim
- geninitramfs: -o, --overlay, suspend2 support?

